# NavigationWizard — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/navigation-wizard.css`

## CSS Classes

### Base
- `.acko-wizard` — `display: flex; align-items: flex-start` — horizontal step row
- `.acko-wizard-vertical` — column layout
- `.acko-wizard-compact` — dot-based progress

### Step (horizontal)
- `.acko-wizard-step` — `display: contents`
- `.acko-wizard-step-body` — flex-col, center-aligned, `gap: var(--scale-8)`, `flex-shrink: 0`, column layout (circle on top, label below)
- `.acko-wizard-step-body-clickable` — `cursor: pointer`

### Circle
- `.acko-wizard-circle` — `28×28px`, `border-radius: var(--radius-full)`, `font-size: 14px`, `font-weight: 600`, `font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums`
- Button element: `cursor: pointer` when enabled, `cursor: default` when disabled

### Circle States

| Status | Background | Color | Border | Shadow |
|--------|-----------|-------|--------|--------|
| `.acko-wizard-circle-upcoming` | transparent | `--color-wizard-upcoming-text` | `2px solid --color-wizard-upcoming-border` | — |
| `.acko-wizard-circle-current` | `--color-wizard-active-bg` | `--color-wizard-active-text` | none | `inset 0 -1px 2px 0 --color-wizard-active-shadow-bottom, inset 0 1px 1px 0 --color-wizard-active-shadow-top` |
| `.acko-wizard-circle-completed` | `--color-wizard-done-bg` | `--color-wizard-done-text` | none | — |
| `.acko-wizard-circle-error` | `--color-error-text` | `--color-on-primary` | none | — |

### Label Block (horizontal)
- `.acko-wizard-label-block` — flex-col, center-aligned, `gap: 2px`
- `.acko-wizard-label` — `font-size: 14px`, `font-weight: 500`, `text-align: center`
- `.acko-wizard-label-upcoming` — `color: --color-wizard-upcoming-text`
- `.acko-wizard-label-current` — `color: --color-text-default`
- `.acko-wizard-label-completed` — `color: --color-text-default`
- `.acko-wizard-label-error` — `color: --color-error-text`
- `.acko-wizard-description` — `font-size: --font-caption-size`, `color: --color-text-secondary`, `max-width: 120px`

### Connector (horizontal)
- `.acko-wizard-connector` — `width: 60px`, `height: 2px`, `margin: 0 var(--scale-8)`, `margin-top: 13px` (aligned to circle center)
- `.acko-wizard-connector-default` — `--color-wizard-connector-upcoming`
- `.acko-wizard-connector-completed` — `--color-wizard-connector-done`

### Vertical Variant
- `.acko-wizard-step-left` — flex-col, center-aligned (holds circle + vertical connector)
- `.acko-wizard-vertical-connector` — `width: 2px`, `flex: 1`, `min-height: 24px`, `margin: var(--scale-4) 0`
- `.acko-wizard-step-content` — `padding-bottom: var(--scale-16)`
- `.acko-wizard-vertical-label` — same font as horizontal, status-based color classes
- `.acko-wizard-vertical-description` — `--font-caption-size`, `--color-text-secondary`, `margin-top: 2px`

### Compact Variant
- `.acko-wizard-compact-dot` — `8×8px`, `border-radius: 50%`
- Dot status classes: `-upcoming` (connector-upcoming bg), `-current` (active bg + `0 0 0 3px --color-primary-ring`), `-completed` (done bg), `-error` (error-text bg)
- `.acko-wizard-compact-label` — `14px`, `font-weight: 500`, `--color-text-default`
- `.acko-wizard-compact-count` — caption size, `--color-text-secondary`, `margin-left: auto`

### Transitions
All color/shadow/border changes: `200ms ease`

## Semantic Tokens Used (defined in `tokens.css`)

| Token | Light | Dark |
|-------|-------|------|
| `--color-wizard-active-bg` | `--purple-500` | `--purple-600` |
| `--color-wizard-active-text` | `--grey-50` | `--grey-white` |
| `--color-wizard-active-shadow-top` | `--purple-400` | `--purple-500` |
| `--color-wizard-active-shadow-bottom` | `--purple-700` | `--purple-800` |
| `--color-wizard-done-bg` | `--purple-200` | `--purple-700` |
| `--color-wizard-done-text` | `--purple-600` | `--purple-300` |
| `--color-wizard-upcoming-border` | `--grey-250` | `--grey-500` |
| `--color-wizard-upcoming-text` | `--grey-350` | `--grey-450` |
| `--color-wizard-connector-done` | `--purple-200` | `--purple-700` |
| `--color-wizard-connector-upcoming` | `--grey-250` | `--grey-500` |

## Dark Theme
Automatic via semantic token remapping — no `[data-theme="dark"]` overrides needed in CSS.
